response.explain: The error occurred because the suitcase was not registered before trying to put the hamburger inside it. The registration of the suitcase is necessary to interact with it.
response.subtask:
(1) Register the hamburger.
(2) Register the suitcase.
(3) Put the hamburger into the suitcase.
(4) Register the water bottle.
(5) Grasp the water bottle.
(6) Put the water bottle into the suitcase.
(7) Grasp the suitcase.
(8) Put the suitcase into the car.
